Definition: the tiresome but essential details that must be taken care of and tasks that must be performed in running an organization
Example: he sets policy and leaves all the administrivia to his assistant
Synonyms: running, the, tiresome, but, essential, details, that, must, be, taken, care, of, and, tasks, performed, in, an, organization, he, sets, policy, leaves, all, to, his, assistant
Category: noun.act
